    HCollection
    A collection represents a group of objects, known as its elements.
    HIterator
    An iterator over a collection.
    HList
    An ordered collection (also known as a sequence).
    HListIterator
    An iterator for lists that allows the programmer to traverse the list in either direction, modify the list during iteration, and obtain the iterator's current position in the list.
    IteratorAdapter
    Adapter class to provide an implementation of the HIterator interface for an HList.
    ListAdapter
    A ListAdapter class that implements the HList interface using a Vector as the underlying implementation.
    ListIteratorAdapter
    ListIteratorAdapter adapts a Vector to the HListIterator interface.
    SubList
